summary:
At Dutch & Such we run online and on-site language training. We offer Dutch language and Inburgering Diploma courses to internationals living in the Netherlands. We also offer Business English training to professionals as well as Legal English training for professionals in law. Nick Walker is fully committed to language training. He's passionate about languages and education technology. Nick's mission is to serve his students' learning needs, above and beyond the call of duty. 

In addition to language training, Nick Walker works as a translator (Dutch to English). He has been working as a freelance translator since 2001. The main areas of translation expertise include Marketing, Advertising, Architecture, Art, Education, and History. 

Clients of Dutch & Such include 180Amsterdam, ABN AMRO, Ace & Tate, Allen & Overy, Amstel Hotel, Blast Radius, BNP Paribas Investment Partners, Booking.com, Forrester Research, Funda.nl, Hoyng Rokh, ICL Europe, IKEA, International School of Amsterdam, Monsterboard.nl, Mr Marvis, Rainforest Alliance (UTZ), Royal Tropical Institute, UN Studio, Valtech, VBAT and Wieden & Kennedy.
